data.description: Mid 19th century, French Second Empire architecture featuring a Mansard roof. Tons of space here. Formal foyer, living and dining rooms. Two living areas. One has the exit to the back yard, covered patio, pergola, pool and out building. Electric gated drive.  Larger den with gas log fire place, built ins, half bathroom and fifth private bedroom access. One bedroom and full bathroom on the main level. Master suite and two additional bedrooms upstairs. Plenty of separation for peace and privacy.
